RECOGNIZE GEMS: Judging precious stones by eye

Category: Trade
Base skill: 30% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Identifying precious and semi-precious stones on sight, telling a
real gem from a convincing fake, and roughly judging a stone's
quality and worth without lab equipment. Useful to jewelers, fences,
and anyone who deals in stolen or traded valuables.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, appraise goods, barter
